ActFood and Drugs Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1389 - SPECIFIED RISK MATERIAL) by establishing a definition for specified risk material (SRM) and by prohibiting the sale or import for sale of food products containing SRM except for countries considered bovine spongiform encephalopathy free.
